T*
(- Core Focus: The main idea the learner must understand in this lesson: transcription,) Tj
T*
(translation, and the role of ribosomes.) Tj
T*
(- Application: The point where the explanation is used in practice, such as following) Tj
T*
(how a DNA code leads to a protein.) Tj
T*
(- Common Error: A repeated learner difficulty in this topic, for example mixing DNA and) Tj
T*
(RNA roles.) Tj
